title: Border Deal, SALT, Green New Deal Vote

description:
Kevin discusses the proposed the bipartisan border funding agreement, Mitch McConnell's planned vote on the Green New Deal and US/Chiina trade talks with guests Mattie Duppler, Senior Fellow at the National Taxpayers Union and Democratic Strategist Andrew Feldman.
